events.name: DevFest 2018

venue.name: The Frontier
venue.address_1: 800 Park Offices Dr, Research Triangle Park, NC 27709

events.description:
As part of GDG DevFest 2018 GDG RTP is hosting a ML focused DevFest. We will have two presentations and then we will start the MLCC (Machine Learning Crash Course) half day agenda. This is online and it has a Google colab portion using TensorFlow with online notebooks.

AGENDA:
4:00 PM Registration & Welcome. Install Software.
5:00 PM Start of session - Modern ML Slides
5:30 PM Introduction to ML Slides
6:00 PM MLCC
9:00 PM Closing

Please review the CoC here : https://www.meetup.com/GDG-Cloud-RTP/about/
events.how_to_find_us: At 4:00pm look for us in the lobby and at 5:00pm in the Fusion room.
